(1, 55, 'HOME_ARTICLE', 'home-article', '<p class="txt1">Welcome to Black Rhino Resort</p>\r\n<p class="txt2">Black Rhino GAME Lodge is a hidden treasure set amongst the trees of an old Tamboti forest, at the foot of an ancient volcanic crater that today, comprises one of South Africa’s most exciting Big 5 eco-tourism destinations, the greater Pilanesberg National Park.</p>\r\n<div class="grid_8">\r\n<div class="grid_4"><a href="/blackrhino/accommodation-rates"><img class="img1" src="images/home_1.jpg" alt="" /></a>\r\n<h3>Accomodation</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_4"><a href="/blackrhino/gallery"><img class="img1" src="images/home_2.jpg" alt="" /></a>\r\n<h3>Gallery</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_4"><a href="/blackrhino/contact-us"><img class="img1" src="images/home_3.jpg" alt="" /></a>\r\n<h3>Location</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_4"><a href="/blackrhino/about-us"><img class="img1" src="images/home_4.jpg" alt="" /></a>\r\n<h3>Pilansberg Park</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="grid_9 alpha">\r\n<div class="grid_4"><img class="img2" src="images/home_5.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<p class="textcolor">Special Offer!</p>\r\n<div class="wrapper_special">\r\n<div class="box_offer">\r\n<p class="textsize">SA Residents book 7 days prior to arrival and save!</p>\r\n<p class="text-size">R 2 645 per person single per night and R 1,765.00 per person sharing per night.</p>\r\n<p class="text">Rates are per person per night and include accommodation, three meals, two GAME drives and VAT at 14%. Rates exclude gate entry fees, beverages and items of a personal nature. Minimum two night stay required over weekends, i.e. Friday and Saturday night. Valid for SA residents only and subject to availability.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_5 alpha_booking">\r\n<h2>booking form</h2>\r\n{loadposition booking}\r\n<div class="wrapper_special">\r\n<div class="box_offer book">\r\n<p class="tel">Tel: +27 11 516 4367</p>\r\n<p class="email">