(4, 58, 'ACCOMMODATION & RATES_ARTICLE', 'accommodation-rates-article', '<div class="wrapper accom">\r\n<h2 class="gurant">You are Guaranteed A Wonderful Bush Experience!</h2>\r\n<img class="img4 image" src="images/accomodation_1.jpg" alt="" />\r\n<p>We offer 5 Star Quality for an affordable rate. Our price includes Luxury Accommodation, Delicious Meals, 2 Game Drives, Great Game Viewing, Exceptional Bird Watching. You are guaranteed a wonderful bush experience.</p>\r\n<p>A top class chef caters for all your exquisite meals in an atmospheric restaurant. Both the bar and the restaurant open out onto the viewing deck, so you are always close to nature.</p>\r\n<p>Children of all ages are welcome!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wrapper accom_type">\r\n<h2>ACCOMMODATION TYPES</h2>\r\n<div class="col"><img class="img4" src="images/aboutus_10.png" alt="" />\r\n<p>Black Rhino Game Lodge boasts 14 very spacious and luxuriously appointed free-standing bedroom suites to ensure that you will go wild in style. Each comfortable air-conditioned suite offers a T.V., hot beverage facility, and private patio that opens out into the bush.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col"><img class="img4" src="images/aboutus_11.png" alt="" />\r\n<p>Black Rhino Game Lodge boasts 14 very spacious and luxuriously appointed free-standing bedroom suites to ensure that you will go wild in style. Each comfortable air-conditioned suite offers a T.V., hot beverage facility, and private patio that opens out into the bush. The designer bathroom opens out onto a totally secluded outdoor shower.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col"><img class="img4" src="images/aboutus_12.png" alt="" />\r\n<p>The 4 Family Suites are situated at the Satelite Camp approximately 700 metres from the Main Lodge. The Camp has its own pool and although there are no TV’s in the rooms there is a central lounge with TV.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 2, '2014-11-20 07:57:01', 939, '', '2014-12-15 12:55:03', 939, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '201