(6, 60, 'CONTACT US_ARTICLE', 'contact-us-article', '<div class="container_16">\r\n<div class="grid_16">\r\n<div class="wrapper contact">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h2>Location</h2>\r\n<figure class="img_inner">\r\n<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d230960.75083042379!2d27.08913!3d-25.24494900000001!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x1ebc2b5c6868323f%3A0xa2556e990fe47531!2sPilanesberg+National+Park!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1418280925999" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"></iframe>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h2>Directions</h2>\r\n<p>33km from Sun City | 150km from Johannesburg</p>\r\n<p>BY AIR:</p>\r\n<p class="contact-text">Fly to Lanseria or OR Tambo International Airports.</p>\r\n<p>BY ROAD:</p>\r\n<p class="contact-text">Travel along the N4 and take the R510 right to Sun City. From the gate of Sun City continue traveling in the direction of Rustenburg for approximately 4kms on the R565. At the stop street, turn right and travel approximately 30kms on the Madikwe road where you will find the entrance of Black Rhino Game Reserve on your right hand side. It is a tar road all the way to the entrance.</p>\r\n<p>Take the N4 Hi-way to Sun City - This road leads onto the R556. You will pass Sun City on your right hand side. Travel to the 4 way stop and turn right onto the R565. Travel on this road R565 for approximately 28km. Black Rhino Game Lodge is on your Right hand side - marked with a large white board BLACK RHINO GAME RESERVE</p>\r\n<p>When you reach Sun City - Please give us a call on 083 297 5020.</p>\r\n<p>GPS Co-ordinates: S25 deg. 10.910’ | E26 deg. 57.320’</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h2>Contact Information</h2>\r\n<table>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr><th colspan="2">BOOKING AGENTS CONTACT DETAILS:</th></tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tel:</td>\r\n<td>+27 11 516 4367</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Fax:</td>\r\n<td>+27 11 463 3713</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Email:</td>\r\n<td>res@extraordinary.co.za</