(121, 109, 'Book Rules', '', '<div class="book">\r\n<h2>Booking Rules</h2>\r\n<div class="book_rules">\r\n<div class="num_section">1</div>\r\n<div class="box2">\r\n<p>Rates are quoted per person per night, excluding transfers, beverages and gate entry fees which are currently R80 per person per night subject to change.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="book_rules">\r\n<div class="num_section">2</div>\r\n<div class="box2">\r\n<p><label>Child Policy:</label>Children under 12 years of age can be accommodated with parents in the same room. The lodge has a limited number of extra beds so it is subject to availability.</p>\r\n<p><label>0-5 years:</label>Complimentary when sharing with full paying adults, maximum of 2 children sharing with 2 adults.</p>\r\n<p><label>6-11 years:</label>Pay published child rate when sharing with two full paying adults, maximum of 2 children sharing with 2 adults permitted on a game drive at management’s discretion.</p>\r\n<p><label>12 Years and older:</label>Considered as adults and accommodated in their own rooms. Pay full rates.</p>\r\n<p><label>Triple Sharing:</label>Not applicable, rooms accommodate a maximum of 2 adults and 2 children under the age of 12 years.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="testi-monial">\r\n<h2>Testimonials</h2>\r\n<div class="testimonial"><label>Great place to stay!</label>\r\n<p>“We visited and stayed here at the start of our South African holiday and had a great time. The room was great, the meals very good and the two safaris we did were great. We would highly recommend this place.”</p>\r\n<p class="testi">Michael-Helen Launceston, Australia</p>\r\n<label>Safari in Style</label>\r\n<p>Beautiful upmarket lodge. The staff were very friendly and helpful and made sure we had everything we needed. Our room was stunning - in fact we''ve been back 3 times and had the same beautifully decorated, spacious room. We loved the setting - surrounded by thorn trees and bush. The were never a disappointed and close encounters with the with lion, elephant and rhino allowed for great memories to be captured.</p>\r\n<p class="testi">Nash family</p>\r\n<label>Great place to stay!</label>\r\n<p>“We visited and stayed here at the start of our South African holiday and had a great time. The room was great, the meals very good and the two safaris we did were great. We would highly recommend this place.”</p>\r\n<p class="testi">Michael-Helen Launceston, Australia</p>\r\n<label>Safari in Style</label>\r\n<p>Beautiful upmarket lodge. The staff were very friendly and helpful and made sure we had everything we needed. Our room was stunning - in fact we''ve been back 3 times and had the same beautifully decorated, spacious room. We loved the setting - surrounded by thorn trees and bush. The were never a disappointed and close encounters with the with lion, elephant and rhino allowed for great memories to be captured.</p>\r\n<p class="testi">Nash family</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 1, 'ratesandrules', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 0, '{"prepare_content":"0","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":" rules","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static","module_tag":"div","bootstrap_size":"0","header_tag":"h3","header_class":"","style":"0"}', 0, '*'),
