-6\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-6 image\\"><p>Photo Coming Soon<\\/p><\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"about_heading\\">Chefs<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"pos\\">Marelize Viljoen (Head Chef), Casper Eygelaar, Tish Moyo.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"about_text\\">Our chefs are extremely diverse and work together to ensure that every meal is of top quality and appealing to guests from all over the world, and ensure that all dietary requirements is adhere to.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"wrapper about_mid\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-4\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-4 image\\"><p>Photo Coming Soon<\\/p><\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"about_heading\\">Bar attendants<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-4\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-4 image\\"><p>Photo Coming Soon<\\/p><\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"about_heading\\">Waiters<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-4\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-4 image\\"><p>Photo Coming Soon<\\/p><\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"about_heading\\">Housekeepers<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"wrapper\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-8 about_accom\\">\\r\\n<h2>Accomodation<\\/h2>\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-2\\"><a href=\\"\\/blackrhino\\/index.php\\/accommodation-rates\\"><img class=\\"img4\\" src=\\"images\\/aboutus_10.png\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-2\\"><a href=\\"\\/blackrhino\\/index.php\\/accommodation-rates\\"><img class=\\"img4\\" src=\\"images\\/aboutus_11.png\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-2\\"><a href=\\"\\/blackrhino\\/index.php\\/accommodation-rates\\"><img class=\\"img4\\" src=\\"images\\/aboutus_12.png\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"col-md-4 about_accom\\">\\r\\n<h2>facilities<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><a href=\\"\\/blackrhino\\/index.php\\/accommodation-rates\\">Bar and restaurant with deck<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><a href=\\"\\/blackrhino\\/index.php\\/accommodation-rates\\">Game drives and viewing<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><a href=\\"\\/blackrhino\\/index.php\\/accommodation-rates\\">Bird watching<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><a href=\\"\\/blackrhino\\/index.php\\/accommodation-rates\\">Swimming Pool<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"last\\"><a href=\\"\\/blackrhino\\/index.php\\/accommodation-rates\\">Laundry Service<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"area\\">\\r\\n<h2>Surrounding attractions<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p><a href=\\"\\/blackrhino\\/index.php\\/accommodation-rates\\">Golf (Sun City), Tour of the lost city , Elephant-back safaris , Balloon Trip over the Pilanesberg<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"2","created":"2014-11-20 07:56:08","created_by":"939","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-12-18 11:37:30","modified_by":"939","checked_out":"939","checked_out_time":"2014-12-18 11:27:57","publish_up":"2014-11-20 07:56:08","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\":\\"\\",\\"show_hits\\":\\"\\",\\"show_noauth\\":\\"\\",\\"urls_position\\":\\"\\",\\"